description:
Playful animations enhance a classic, captivating story with loads of interactive graphics
 Dress up Cinderella and help her get ready to meet Prince Charming at the Royal Ball 
 Insert your own dialogue into the story using our voice-recording microphone

The classic fairytale of Cinderella comes alive like never before. Children can interact with tons of characters including the glass slipper, pumpkin and mice that all move about with the touch of a finger.  Silly sound effects will keep children of all ages entertained and engaged in this beautifully animated and timeless tale. Discover multiple activities on every page including puzzles and games. Tap the game icons on the screen to find loads of extra fun on every page.  

What's inside:
> Jigsaw puzzles - Awesome puzzles enhance the story and promote critical thinking skills 
> Paint-a-Picture - Dozens of coloring pages and paints 
> Counting - 1 to 10 counting game is cool and fun 
> Match It - Fire up your child’s memory skills with this smart activity! 
> More fun & educational games inside!
> Dress up Cinderella and help her get ready for the Royal Ball
> 10 pages of beautiful HD illustrations enhance a rich narrative
> Animated characters and fun, lively sound effects
> Enjoy numerous activities, puzzles and games
> Voice-recording microphone allows kids to record their own dialogue for multiple characters.

This interactive storybook of the classic Cinderella story brings the fairytale to life through its vivid animations and engaging interactions.  It is sure to appeal to children from toddlers to grade school kids and provide endless hours of enjoyment.

Features:
> “Play” - automatically reads each page of the story to you.
> “Read it Myself” - allows you to control the reading yourself.
> “Auto Play” - automatically reads the entire story to you.
> “Dress Up” - find dress up pages as you read and play.
